headline: Raymond James Considers AT&T (T) a Top Large-Cap Total Return Opportunity
summary: AT&T Inc. (NYSE:T) is one of the best value stocks in Goldman Sachs’ portfolio. On September 18, Frank Louthan, an analyst at Raymond James, raised the price target on the stock from $31 to $33 and maintained his Buy rating.
